        <span content="2010-11-09" class="main-meta">2010-11-09 09:23:31</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4456121/">安妮宝贝</a></h2>

                <div id="review_4456121_short" class="review-short" data-rid="4456121">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        对于单身者，自身磁场不强者，不建议看这样的书，看过书再看世界，觉得很灰暗，人生应该多彩，积极向上，你说呢

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4456121-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

